#. type: Plain text
#: ../Documentation-sedout/technical/hash-function-transition.txt:667
msgid "The next step is supporting fetches and pushes to SHA-1 repositories:"
msgstr "次のステップは、 SHA-1 リポジトリへのフェッチとプッシュのサポートです:"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../Documentation-sedout/technical/hash-function-transition.txt:669
